10. Cross-Engine Reference Envelope
{
  "engine": "DRE",
  "artifact_type": "hypothesis",
  "artifact_id": "UUID",
  "artifact_version": 3
}
CWP never mutates referenced artifacts.
11. Migration & Replay Strategy
  additive schema changes only
  events and decisions are immutable
  projections rebuilt from ledgers
